Come join other UC Santa Barbara Gauchos here on Myspace!!! UC Santa Barbara Gauchos (for current students & alumni) UC Santa Barbara Gauchos Group (for EVERYBODY!!!!!!!) Mission Statement: This is a place where all current students and alumni of UC Santa Barbara can come together and share memories, pictures, advice, and information regarding upcoming parties, events on campus, the best professors/courses, and pretty much to discuss anything else that goes on at UCSB. General Info: The campus of the University of California, Santa Barbara is located in the beautiful city of Santa Barbara. The campus stretches across 989 acres along the Pacific Ocean coastline overlooking the Santa Ynez Mountains. UCSB is the party school with an impressive academic reputation. The students know how to have a good time but also know how to take care of business in the classroom.
